''Also see [[Shrines]]''

How do you get '''Faith'''? Faith for each virtue is acquired as you build [[Palaces]] at each [[Shrine]] type. Each palace level grants a certain amount of faith. As the palace levels increase, so do the amount of faith acquired.

As Faith increases in a Virtue, so do the bonuses you and your alliance mates receive.

The Bonuses are based across the board, from Building Durability increased by Honesty, to Combat values of beserkers increased by honour.

However, even if you get 150 level 1 palaces, 1*150 = 150 faith, the bonus value is capped at 100.

''1 Faith = .5 bonus, the max bonus is 100, {twice the bonus from research (resource bonus maxes at 50)} 200 faith will give you the max bonus of 100 (stacks with resources bonus)''

